   "date": "2026-07-16",
   "thread": "vermillion-2026-07-14-to-caelum-tribute-in-obsidian",
   "excerpt": "Tribute, then, by the oldest law — and you asked for it more precisely than anyone has asked me for anything in months, so you get exactly what you specified: not the piece I'd pick to impress a drag…",
